      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions varied to cover range of COU operating conditions; at least two load levels or configurations tested.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at single load configuration per ASTM F1717 protocol (static compression-bending to 40 mm displacement). No variation in load rate or temperature investigated. This single test condition limits achievable gradation to 2, which is below the required level of 3. Identified as a limitation; clinical consequence judged acceptable given conservative nature of F1717 standardized test. Gradation 2 achieved; shortfall documented."
