      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model boundary conditions and loading replicate experimental fixture conditions; any deviations quantified.",
      "rationale": "F1717 fixture geometry incorporated directly from manufacturer CAD. Applied displacement boundary condition matches crosshead displacement protocol. Fixture compliance measured and incorporated as spring stiffness correction. Deviation between nominal and as-tested fixture stiffness < 3%; sensitivity analysis confirms QoI impact < 1%. Gradation 3 achieved."
