      "rationale": "Three QoIs compared: construct stiffness (4.2%, E/uval=0.81), yield force (7.8%, E/uval=1.43), force at 40 mm (5.1%, E/uval=0.97). All within pre-established acceptance bounds. Validation uncertainty includes experimental repeatability (two laboratories), measurement uncertainty, and model input uncertainty combined in quadrature. Gradation 3 achieved."
